body: Hi, I am a french video maker, I made subtitles on this video, this one which worked the best on my channel ^^ I would like yo know what do you think about it, and if it would be worth it to make a new one but with english vocal. thanks :)

replies.body: Looks like a cool video, i think one with english vocals would be beneficial, as it is hard to follow what is on screen as well as read the subtitles. But it seems pretty cool!
Would be nicer to look at if the low res diamond rank icon went over the moose mask and the horns awkwardly popped up...
